    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Menu\nEmirates",
      "San Francisco - Dubai\nJuice\nFruit\nMain Course\nBread\nBeverages\nBreakfast\nFresh fruit juice\nFresh seasonal fruit\nFruit yoghurt\nMushroom omelette\ncreamy mushroom omelette, served with grilled chicken\nand apple sausages, tomato filled with spinach and\nsautéed potatoes with onions\nBaingan bhajia\nzucchini chicken roll, served with deep fried eggplant,\naloo bhaji and paratha\nFrench toast\npan-fried toast slices with egg coating, served with\ncaramelised apples and maple syrup\nCheese selection\nwhich includes cambozola, chaumes and Emmenthal,\naccompanied with mixed olives, tomato and cucumber\nBread basket\na variety of freshly baked breads, croissants and\nbreakfast pastries, served with butter and preserves\nTea\nCeylon, China, Earl Grey, Camomile\nCoffee\nfreshly brewed, decaffeinated, espresso and cappuccino\njohal\nUnica"
    ],
